────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
> ./cukes-vhs generate --help
Usage of generate:
  -all
        Generate for all translatable scenarios
  -config-source string
        Path to config tape file (default "demos/config.tape")
  -feature string
        Filter by feature name
  -features string
        Directory containing .feature files (default "features/")
  -output string
        Output directory (required)
  -scenario string
        Filter by scenario name
  -scenarios-dir string
        Directory containing VHS-only .feature files (default "demos/scenarios/")
  -timeout int
        Per-tape render timeout in seconds (default 120)
  -verbose
        Verbose output
